i:3.0.0`.\n\nChanged:\n\n- `tests/src/jakarta.enterprise/jakarta.enterprise.cdi-api/3.0.0/build.gradle`\n\nWhat changed:\n\n- Configured the JVM `test` task to run with a Java 21 launcher.\n- Enabled dynamic SecurityManager installation with:\n\n```groovy\n-Djava.security.manager=allow\n```\n\nThis allows the existing `SecurityActionsTest` path that installs a `SecurityManager` to execute the privileged branch in `jakarta.enterprise.util.SecurityActions.getDeclaredMethods`, reaching:\n\n```java\nAccessController.doPrivileged(\n        (PrivilegedAction<Method[]>) () -> clazz.getDeclaredMethods()\n);\n```\n\nand therefore covering the remaining call site:\n\n- `SecurityActions.lambda$getDeclaredMethods$1(SecurityActions.java:54)`\n\nI did not run tests or compile locally, per workflow rules.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c090013604f2c400169fc507fffbc819f8b716199d3368766\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 456, "output": 1047, "cacheRead": 33792, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35295, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778143347510, "responseId": "resp_0c090013604f2c400169fc50746770819fa6685b50fa6caf80"}, "toolResults": []}
